g.text: 4540 Ma. Earth forms from the solar protoplanetary disk
3480 Ma. earliest indications of life on land
3465 Ma. earliest direct undisputed evidence of life
380 - 375 Ma. first tetrapods evolve and venture onto land
360 - 260 Ma. Late Paleozoic icehouse (Karoo ice age)
68 - 66 Ma. Tyrannosaurus rex roams the Earth
